-- 1) Tabela de carros
CREATE TABLE "Car" (
  "CarId"        SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  "CodCar"       INTEGER     NOT NULL,
  "Brand"        TEXT        NOT NULL,
  "Name"         TEXT        NOT NULL,
  "Value"        NUMERIC(12,2),
  "Year"         INTEGER,
  "YearModel"    INTEGER,
  "Km"           INTEGER,
  "Tracting"     TEXT,
  "Door"         INTEGER, 
  "Bodywork"     TEXT,
  "Plate"        TEXT,
  "TypePlate"    TEXT,
  "Cambium"      TEXT,
  "Fuel"         TEXT,
  "Description"  TEXT,
  "Color"        TEXT,
  "ObjectImage"  TEXT    -- URL ou JSON com paths
);

-- 2) Tabela de opções
CREATE TABLE "Options" (
  "OptionsId"     SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  "ObjectOptions" TEXT    -- JSON ou texto descritivo da opção
);

-- 3) Relacionamento Car ↔ Options (N:N)
CREATE TABLE "carToOptions" (
  "RowId"      SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  "CarId"      INTEGER NOT NULL REFERENCES "Car"("CarId")    ON DELETE CASCADE,
  "OptionsId"  INTEGER NOT NULL REFERENCES "Options"("OptionsId") ON DELETE CASCADE,
  UNIQUE ("CarId","OptionsId")
);

-- 4) Tabela de vendedores
CREATE TABLE "Seller" (
  "SellerId"         SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  "Cpf"              TEXT,
  "Name"             TEXT,
  "Cellphone"        TEXT,
  "Address"          TEXT,
  "BankAccnt"        TEXT,
  "BloodType"        TEXT,
  "ObjectFamilyData" TEXT,   -- JSON com dados da família
  "Function"         TEXT,
  "Mail"             TEXT,
  "Linkedin"         TEXT,
  "Instagram"        TEXT,
  "EntryDay"         DATE,
  "PayDay"           DATE
);

-- 5) Relacionamento Car ↔ Seller (N:N)
CREATE TABLE "carToSeller" (
  "RowId"    SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  "CarId"    INTEGER NOT NULL REFERENCES "Car"("CarId")     ON DELETE CASCADE,
  "SellerId" INTEGER NOT NULL REFERENCES "Seller"("SellerId") ON DELETE CASCADE,
  UNIQUE ("CarId","SellerId")
);

-- 6) Tabela de dados da Vivare
CREATE TABLE "VivareData" (
  "VivareId"         SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  "Instagram"       TEXT,
  "Facebook"        TEXT,
  "Mail"            TEXT,
  "Tour"            TEXT,
  "Address"         TEXT,
  "Phone"           TEXT,
  "PresentationText" TEXT
);

-- 7) Tabela de usuários da Vivare
CREATE TABLE "UserVivare" (
  "UserId"     SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  "Mail"       TEXT    UNIQUE NOT NULL,
  "Password"   TEXT    NOT NULL,
  "Name"       TEXT,
  "Function"   TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE "Highlight" (
  "HighlightId"   UUID    PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid(),
  "CarId"         INTEGER,
  "CarName"       TEXT,
  "CarDescription" TEXT,
  "Year"          INTEGER,
  "YearModel"     INTEGER,  
  "Value"         INTEGER,
  "ObjectImageCar"   TEXT
);
